OL,3,CMan who murdered stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf jailed
OL,6,FA man who strangled his stepmother to
OL,7,Fdeath with her headscarf has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FAbdul Sami, now 22, searched
OL,11,Finheritance websites, including one
OL,12,Fwith the question "does a killer
OL,13,Finherit from the victim's estate?"
OL,14,Fbefore attacking 41-year-old Rizwana
OL,15,FKousar.
OL,17,FMrs Kousar was found unconscious in
OL,18,Fthe bath at her home on Kensington
OL,19,FRoad in Bradford on 15 August 2023.
OL,20,FShe died two days later.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
