CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774293066
OL,3,CMan who murdered stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf jailed
OL,6,FSami, of Mannheim Road, claimed he had
OL,7,Ffound her in the bath before calling
OL,8,F999 and later told police she had a
OL,9,Fred mark on her neck because he had
OL,10,Fremoved her scarf to perform CPR.
OL,12,FSami, now 22, was convicted of murder
OL,13,Ffollowing a trial at Bradford Crown
OL,14,FCourt.
OL,16,FHe was jailed for life with a minimum
OL,17,Fterm of 14 years and 91 days.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
