FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774293066
OL,3,CMan who murdered stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard a statement from Mrs
OL,7,FKousar's sister-in-law Mariam Afzal,
OL,8,Fwho said: "That she is gone is
OL,9,Funimaginable.
OL,11,F"Her loss has impacted every day and
OL,12,Fwill do so forever."
OL,14,FAddressing Sami, Ms Afzal said: "You
OL,15,Ftook her life for what? Money? And you
OL,16,Flied over and over and over. You tried
OL,17,Fto cover your disgusting actions to
OL,18,Fmake it look like an accident when it
OL,19,Fwas pre-planned and you have shown no
OL,20,Fremorse.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774293066
OL,3,CMan who murdered stepmum with
OL,4,Cheadscarf jailed
OL,6,F"I can't help wonder what her final
OL,7,Fmoments were like. Was she in pain?
OL,8,FWas she scared? Did she realise what
OL,9,Fwas happening to her? You treated her
OL,10,Flike she had no worth.
OL,12,F"It is unbearable to think of that and
OL,13,Fhow you were the last person she
OL,14,Fsaw... We will never forgive you."
OL,16,FSami showed no emotion as he was
OL,17,Fsentenced.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
